{"tid":831563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港工程世界第一","createTime":"2018-09-22T05:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T05:39:00.000Z","uid":126320,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de6e5c6fc70e5331508517510a5620b4c6878aa4","tid":831563,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"超強颱風「山竹」早前吹襲香港，造成廣泛破壞，前天文台台長林超英出席電台節目時表示，「山竹」襲港令他最大觸動是零死亡，這是天氣預測人員「夢寐以求」的結果，更可以是「世界新聞」。對於風後首個上班日交通大亂，他建議香港設立網上平台，讓市民報告路面情況，達至每日都有一張顯示全港路況的地圖。<br />\n<br />\n林超英讚揚，香港在是次風災的表現其實是「世界第一」，要寫文章向行家讚賞香港氣象部門、市民等面對是次風災的態度。他續指，沒有太多國家在受超強颱風吹襲後，出現零死亡，例如颶風「佛羅倫斯」上周登陸美國東岸，亦造成數十人死亡。"},{"pid":"4517f840c3fbab507c77028b5ee1035825afe3f1","tid":831563,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"我城工程巧威威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f1b90abf2b5eed662b9299386c2b9288a1e253","tid":831563,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:31:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78fd545d4543819f33d08c59fef718c58351ac2","tid":831563,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137bba9643bdaf531b9c5551eb7bc547b8efb122","tid":831563,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2725100d6262846f87171bfef08f43bb2f3e242","tid":831563,"uid":202035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"緊係零死亡啦 死左個個都比人話自殺 香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3a909f434729de7381bac383a4a130770ffedb","tid":831563,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2725100d6262846f87171bfef08f43bb2f3e242","tid":831563,"uid":20203